+start), MODIFIED (retry\/resolve IP),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and DELETED (stop+delete) events"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"NodeManager","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" — Discovers Mac nodes by label, maps to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"HTTP API endpoints, periodic health checks","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"MacOSVMResource"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Codable types matching the CRD schema"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The controller is stateless — all state lives in CRD status","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"fields and on the Mac nodes themselves.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Mac-Node-Setup","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Mac Node Setup"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Each Mac node must run ","type":"text"},{"code":"spook serve","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["# Install Spooktacular","brew install --cask spooktacular","","# Create a base VM","spook create base --from-ipsw latest","","# Start the HTTPS API (bind to all interfaces for cluster access)","spook serve --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8484 \\","  --tls-cert \/etc\/spooktacular\/tls\/cert.pem \\","  --tls-key \/etc\/spooktacular\/tls\/key.pem","","# Or install as a service for persistence","sudo spook service install base  # for the base VM"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"bash"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Label Mac nodes in Kubernetes for the controller to discover:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["kubectl label node mac-01 spooktacular.app\/role=mac-host"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"bash"},{"anchor":"Troubleshooting","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Troubleshooting"},{"anchor":"VM-stuck-in-Pending","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"VM stuck in Pending"},{"inlineContent":[{"tex